                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">Additio 2 mentiones ras Sǝbḥat  (ras Sǝbḥat ʾArägawi, b. ca. 1844, d. 1914), with baptismal name Kidanä Maryam, as the donor. The names of his relatives are also mentioned: his mother Wälättä Śǝllase, his wife Wälättä Maryam, his children Gäbrä Ḥǝywät, Wäldä Gäbrǝʾel, ʾArʾaya Śǝllase.&#xD;
